OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Ffine evening, but turning cloudy
OL,7,Facross northern parts of the region
OL,8,Fovernight with a few spots of light
OL,9,Frain over the Peak District. However,
OL,10,Fremaining dry elsewhere with clear
OL,11,Fskies and a mild night.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FStaying cloudy across the far
OL,14,Fnorth, but strong sunshine elsewhere
OL,15,Fwhich could turn hazy at times.
OL,16,FFeeling very warm in the sunshine and
OL,17,Flight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
